description:
Sam Neves, the creator of Heroes 2, says that if God has given you a great idea, you’ve got to go for it with courage. The original Heroes 2 project manager, Arnaldo Oliveira, adds that to see a big project through, you’ve got to keep your eye on the goal but also understand all the smaller steps it takes to get there. 

A team of 20 designers, engineers, content creators, marketers and more worked hard behind the scenes to make Heroes happen. Sam says it’s super important to have A-players that are 100% committed to the mission and success of the project.


Learn more at: https://www.heroesbibletrivia.org/en/
